div.p:
Are you desirous of a guide in this way? here are two offering of themselues, God & Baal; the one will conduct you to the land of Canaan,

         Ios. 1.2. the other will lead you blindfold to Samaria
      2. King. 6.19.. If you follow the one, you wil worship in mount Zion;

         Is. 2.2.3. If the other you, must goe vp to mount Gerizim;

         Ioh. 4.20. and there adore Ieroboams calues,1. King. 12.28.
